- "plummeted into the abyss" refers to tasks that have failed;
- "fingerprints" refers to the unique task hash;
- "remained stuck in the shadows" means the task's status is still marked as 'failed';
- "more than three times" refers to the repetition count of the task in the task_dependencies table.
